== Overview ==
The '''Vulcore Plain''' (also referred to simply as '''Vulcore''') is the primary patrol zone for [[Controller|Controllers]] in the early-to-mid game. Once the site of the now-infamous "Magma" weapons testing range, the Vulcore Plain is two million square miles of some of the most hazardous terrain on earth. The test complex lies somewhere in the centre of the massive, and now constantly active volcanic field. Dangers such as energy storms, military test mines, and magma geysers are commonly encountered. Both the isolation and hazardous terrain make Vulcore a popular location for renegade squads and, in more recent times, gangs of [[Scaven]] hunters.

Vulcore is the first major outland zone available to Controllers and serves as the primary source of [[Mercreds]], [[Crowns]], [[Technology]] segments, and early [[Battle Merit]].

