=== Renegades ===
A rogue bot faction operating across Vulcore. Renegades occupy bases, workshops, and uplink installations. They use blast walls and standard bot chassis.

'''Notable Renegade units:'''
* '''[[Perimeter Wall]]''' — Renegade Wall chassis with Light Wall Effect.
* '''[[Base Wall]]''' — Renegade Wall chassis with Light Wall Effect and BM Adjustment.
* '''[[Siege Wall]]''' — Renegade Blast Wall chassis with [[Quad Argon Lasers]], Light Wall Effect, and BM Adjustment x2. Armed and dangerous.
* '''[[Uplink Controller]]''' — Uplink Controller chassis with [[Bio-Nuclear]] reactor, [[Deflection Grid]], [[Mechanical Obviator]], and [[Weapons Amplifier]] modules.
* '''[[BASE LORD]]''' — [[Leviathan]] chassis with [[Tribolt Hydron]] reactor, [[Argon (Shield)|Argon]] x2 shields, [[EM Syphon]] x2, [[Shield Disruptor|Shield Disrupter]] x2, [[Baron Laser]] x2, [[Baron Battery]] x2, [[EM Pulse Emitter]], [[Flux Channel]]. The Renegade Base Commander (RBC). Defeating it yields Technology segments and significant rewards.
* '''[[BATTLE LORD]]''' — [[Leviathan]] chassis with [[Tribolt Hydron]] reactor, [[Argon Web]] x2 shields, [[Heavy Shield Disruptor]] x2, [[Fire Blade]] x2, [[Pulse Beam]] x2, [[Good Samaritan]], [[Heavy Shield Displacer]], [[EM Wave Emitter]], [[Flux Channel]].
* '''[[DREAD LORD]]''' — [[Leviathan]] chassis with [[Tribolt Hydron]] reactor, [[Argon Web]] x2 shields, [[Shield Neutraliser]] x2, [[Syphon MKII]], [[Pulse Streamer]], [[HR100 Rocket Pack]] x2, [[Baron Battery]] x2, [[Deflection Grid]], [[EM Wave Emitter]].
* '''[[EMPEROR LORD]]''' — [[Leviathan]] chassis with [[Tribolt Hydron]] reactor, [[Argon Web]] x2 shields, [[Pulse Streamer]] x3, [[HR X Rocket Pack]] x5.

=== Fallen ===
A mysterious and malevolent faction encountered in the Lava Fields. The Fallen are arch-enemies of the Angels and offer powerful (but costly) gifts to Controllers with negative alignment.

'''Encounter options (requires negative alignment):'''
* '''Greed''' — 10x cash multiplier. Costs 20 Mercreds and alignment. Stays active until replaced by another cash multiplier.
* '''Coords - Azra''' — Coordinates to Azra's Arena.
* '''Imps''' — 3 Orbiter-chassis bots with 3x TC7 Target Predictor and Baron Battery. Fast, high crit, low defence.
* '''Dark Union''' — Requires −100 alignment. Adds 2 Demons (Bulwark), 2 Fiends (Overseer), and 1 Baal or Beelzebub (Leviathan) to the squad. Grants +180% fire rate, 12% critical, ~1000 projected shield. Comes with a growing curse that drains cash and XP each step without combat.

