=== Angels ===
A mysterious benevolent faction encountered in the Lava Fields. The Angels are arch-enemies of the Fallen and offer gifts to Controllers with positive alignment.

'''Encounter options (requires positive alignment):'''
* '''Enrichment''' — 10x cash multiplier. Costs 10 alignment. Equivalent to Greed for positive-align players. Not affected by Power Storms (though storms attract it).
* '''Clan Aid''' — 10 Construction Notes (CN).
* '''Technology''' — 1 segment each of Magma Tech, Bulwark Tech, and Crusader Tech.
* '''Guardian Angels''' — Requires +50 alignment. Costs 25 alignment. 1–2 Angel bots join the squad for a very long time. Their shields make the squad nearly invincible.

