== Annihilators ==
[[File:Terminus.jpg|right|200px|link=Terminus|The Terminus chassis]]
Annihilators are powerful boss-tier enemies that appear in the [[Sulphur Fields]]. They are described as "mini Termies" — significantly stronger than standard enemies but easier than a [[Terminus]].

'''Key facts:'''
* Appear in the Sulphur Fields during patrol
* Bring Seer-type support units, making them dangerous even for well-equipped squads
* Upon defeat, drop a superweapon based on the Controller's BM:
** Low BM: [[Thermal Dawn]]
** Mid BM: [[Riot Gun]]
** High BM: [[Obliterator]]
* Their kills and deaths are announced on CyCom

'''Annihilator stats:'''
* Chassis: [[Terminus]]
* HP: 10,000
* Speed: 90
* Projected Shield: 23,760
* Reactor: [[Tribolt Hydron]] (3000 energy)
* Shields: [[Argon 400]] x4 (1200 each)
* Weapons: [[Shield Displacer]] x2, [[Riot Gun]] x2, [[LR100 Rocket Pack]], [[Vulcan Cannon]] x2, [[Syphon Elite]]
* Modules: [[Flux Channel]], [[EM Wave Emitter]]

'''TERMINUS (special variant):'''
* Chassis: [[Terminus]]
* HP: 40,000
* Speed: 90
* Weapons: [[Shield Neutraliser]] x2, [[Obliterator]] x2, [[Baron Battery]] x2, [[Fire Blade]], [[Rail-Gun]]
* Reactor: [[Magmatic Pyroclast]] (5000 energy)
* Module: Terminus Core
* Shield: [[Baron Impulse]]

The Terminus is a special bot released by player actions or admins. It grows stronger with each kill it makes. Its kills and death are announced on CyCom. Requires significant drain capability to defeat.

