* Minimum ~750K BM recommended

== Technologies ==

=== Magma Technology ===
Magma Technology is a progressive upgrade system unlocked by collecting Magma Segments. Maximum: 20 segments.

'''Sources of Magma Segments:'''
* Killing Magma Lords (Lord Magmas)
