== Power Storms ==
Power Storms are a hazard unique to the Vulcore Plain. When a Power Storm hits:
* Cash multipliers (Greed/Enrichment) are attracted by storms — storms can strip or reduce multipliers
* Energy drain effects may occur
* The [[Storm Shield]] (purchasable at outposts for 200 Mercreds) provides protection against Power Storms — it still reduces multipliers slightly but prevents full drain and energy loss

'''Storm Shield:''' Costs 200 Mercreds at a Mercenary Outpost. Highly recommended before attempting Greed/Enrichment runs.

