== Crowns ==
Crowns are a special currency found in Vulcore, primarily obtained by:
* Defeating Scaven Matriarchs (Matriarch Crowns mission)
* Sun Ritual (4 Crowns)
* Ice Queen (1 Crown)
* Scaven Burial Mounds (negative alignment penalty)

Crowns are deposited at Mercenary Outposts and converted to Mercreds or used for other purposes. It is recommended to deposit Crowns at the first outpost found before leaving patrol.

